00:00:00.690 --> 00:00:04.680
&gt;&gt; From the Library of
Congress in Washington, DC.

00:00:08.650 --> 00:00:14.050
&gt;&gt; BARD Express: Using
Your Wish List

00:00:14.050 --> 00:00:19.240
&gt;&gt; Judy: Hi, I'm Judy Dixon
Consumer Relations Officer at NLS.

00:00:19.240 --> 00:00:22.410
In this edition of the
BARD Express How-To Series,

00:00:22.410 --> 00:00:25.750
I'm going to cover
using your wish list.

00:00:25.750 --> 00:00:30.270
From the BARD Express Main
Menu select Wish List.

00:00:30.270 --> 00:00:32.650
You will be presented
with a list of the types

00:00:32.650 --> 00:00:35.960
of materials you have
downloaded from BARD.

00:00:35.960 --> 00:00:41.650 position:56%
The contents of your wish list can
also be sorted by Subject or Author.

00:00:41.650 --> 00:00:46.410
In this example I am going to
select All Books and Magazines.

00:00:46.410 --> 00:00:51.700
All of the materials available
on your wish list will present.

00:00:51.700 --> 00:00:56.320
&gt;&gt; NVDA: The Writer:
January 2016, 1 of 3.

00:00:56.320 --> 00:01:00.930
Nano. Author: Cook, Robin, 2 of 3.

00:01:00.930 --> 00:01:04.090
The New Yorker: June 20, 2016.

00:01:04.090 --> 00:01:11.460 position:56%
3 of 3. Download button, Alt plus D.
There is now one item downloading.

00:01:11.460 --> 00:01:14.040
Downloads are complete.

00:01:14.040 --> 00:01:17.970
Wish list: all books and
magazines, two items.

00:01:17.970 --> 00:01:21.530
&gt;&gt; Judy: Once your downloads are
complete your books will be stored

00:01:21.530 --> 00:01:24.580
on your BARD Express
bookshelf until you are ready

00:01:24.580 --> 00:01:26.850
to transfer them to a cartridge.

00:01:26.850 --> 00:01:33.110 position:56%
See the How-to Transfer Materials to
a cartridge video for instructions.

00:01:33.110 --> 00:01:37.750
For additional instructions
on using BARD Express,

00:01:37.750 --> 00:01:41.580 position:56%
see the other videos in this series.

00:01:41.580 --> 00:01:45.450
&gt;&gt; This has been a presentation
of the Library of Congress.

00:01:45.450 --> 00:01:47.820
